name: Giraffe
description: All blankets are fleece on one side and flannel on the other.  They do have ties on two sides but these are just for looks.  All blankets are machine sewn and machine washable/dryable.  They are really thick and super warm! These blankets are great to use as throws on the back of the couch, stroller/crib blankets, travel blankets, or at the foot of your bed.  Choose any pattern, color, or theme.  You can also have it personalized by adding a name.
